    "body": "Problem:  Redrawing in an autocommand that uses an autocommand window\r\n          (more common since 5181984d) can result in flickering.\r\nSolution: Hide autocommand windows.\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-05-30T10:55:17Z",
