            "body": "The \"don't redraw hidden windows\" part is just an internal optimization. An `open_win/set_config` caller just expects the window to not be shown, which doesn't change here, so I'm not sure documenting it is warranted/helpful.\r\n\r\nBut I'll remove all changes related to that issue, missed these sorry.",
