            }
        },
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Without it, we sometimes fail to hide windows from the grid (seemingly if `win_ui_flush(false)` runs before `win_ui_flush(true)`). I'll check if I can find a more appropriate fix for that.",
